rtmouth)|Memorial Field]]. They were a member of the [[Ivy League]]. They finished the season 9\u20131 overall and 6\u20131 in Ivy League play to place three-way tie for the Ivy League title with [[2015 Harvard Crimson football team|Harvard]] and [[2015 Penn Quakers football team|Penn]].\n\n==Schedule==\n{{CFB schedule\n| rankyear = 2015\n| rankdivision = NCAA Division I FCS\n| poll = STATS\n| timezone = Eastern\n\n|{{CFB schedule entry\n| date = September 19\n| time = 12:00 PM\n| w/l = w\n| nonconf = y\n| away = y\n| opponent = [[2015 Georgetown Hoyas football team|Georgetown]]\n| site_stadium = [[Multi-Sport Field]]\n| site_cityst = [[Washington, D.C.|Washington, DC]]\n| tv = [[Campus Insiders]]\n| score = 31\u201310\n| attend = 2,863\n}}\n|{{CFB schedule entry\n| date = September 26\n| time = 7:00 PM\n| w/l = w\n| nonconf = y\n| opponent = [[2015 Sacred Heart Pioneers football team|Sacred Heart]]\n| site_stadium = [[Memorial Field (Dartmouth College)|Memorial Field]]\n| site_cityst = [[Hanover, New Hampshire|Hanover, NH]]\n| tv = \n| score = 49\u20137\n| attend = 7,363\n}}\n|{{CFB schedule entry\n| date = October 3\n| time = 3:30 PM\n| w/l = w\n| away = y\n| opponent = [[2015 Penn Quakers football team|Penn]]\n| site_stadium = [[Franklin Field]]\n| site_cityst = [[Philadelphia|Philadelphia, PA]]\n| tv = \n| score = 41\u201320\n| attend = 4,520\n}}\n|{{CFB schedule entry\n| date = October 10\n| time = 1:30 PM\n| w/l = w\n| homecoming = y\n| opponent = [[2015 Yale Bulldogs football team|Yale]]\n| site_stadium = Memorial Field\n| site_cityst = Hanover, NH\n| tv = [[Fox College Sports|FCS]]\n| score = 35\u20133\n| attend = 11,086\n}}\n|{{CFB schedule entry\n| date = October 17\n| time = 12:00 PM\n| w/l = w\n| nonconf = y\n| away = y\n| opponent = [[2015 Central Connecticut Blue Devils football team|Central Connecticut]]\n| site_stadium = [[Arute Field]]\n| site_cityst = [[New Britain, Connecticut|New Britain, CT]]\n| tv = \n| score = 34\u20137\n| attend = 2,064\n}}\n